{% extends "base.html.j2" %}

{% block title %}
{% if language == 'tr' %}Konumunuz Gönderildi - {{ location_name }}{% elif language == 'en' %}Your Location Has Been Submitted - {{ location_name }}{% else %}Uw Locatie is Ingediend - {{ location_name }}{% endif %}
{% endblock %}

{% block header_subtitle %}
<p>
    {% if language == 'tr' %}
        Konum talebiniz alındı
    {% elif language == 'en' %}
        Your location submission has been received
    {% else %}
        Uw locatie inzending is ontvangen
    {% endif %}
</p>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
{% if language == 'tr' %}
<p>Merhaba {{ user_name }},</p>

<p><strong>{{ location_name }}</strong> için yaptığınız locatie inzending başarıyla alındı. İncelenmesi için admin ekibimize iletildi.</p>

<p>İnceleme süreci genellikle birkaç gün sürer. Sonuç hakkında size e-posta göndereceğiz.</p>

<p>Teşekkürler,<br>Turkspot Ekibi</p>

{% elif language == 'en' %}
<p>Hello {{ user_name }},</p>

<p>Your location submission for <strong>{{ location_name }}</strong> has been successfully received and forwarded to our admin team for review.</p>

<p>The review process usually takes a few days. We will send you an email about the result.</p>

<p>Thank you,<br>The Turkspot Team</p>

{% else %}
<p>Hoi {{ user_name }},</p>

<p>Uw locatie inzending voor <strong>{{ location_name }}</strong> is succesvol ontvangen en doorgestuurd naar ons admin team voor beoordeling.</p>

<p>Het beoordelingsproces duurt meestal een paar dagen. We sturen u een e-mail over het resultaat.</p>

<p>Bedankt,<br>Het Turkspot Team</p>
{% endif %}
{% endblock %}







